'''Smartrac N.V.''' is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] manufacturer of high security [[RFID]] inlays.<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.finanznachrichten.de/nachrichten-2006-07/6700782-smartrac-n-v-plans-ipo-in-july-007.htm | title = SMARTRAC N.V. plans IPO in July | accessdate = 2008-03-24}}</ref> It is the world's largest supplier of inlays for [[ePassport]]s.<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bankkaufmann.com/a-33532-SMARTRAC-ships-10th-million-ePassport-inlay-and-is-the-worldund146s-largest-supplier-for-electronic-passports.html | title = SMARTRAC ships 10th million ePassport inlay and is the world’s largest supplier for electronic passports | accessdate=2009-03-24}}</ref> Since 2006 its shares are listed on the [[Frankfurt Stock Exchange]].
